descriptionHtml:
Some changes to Sneak skill tree to make you a more fearsome assasin, such as:

- Deadly Aim now have 15% chance to paralyze target.
- Change Backstab perk name to Executioner, add two-handed weapon deals 4x sneak damage.
- Shadow Warrior now make you invisible when crouch while not in combat.

Have fun. Critics and input for improvement are welcome.


My other mods:
- Magic Overlord (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14825)
- Shout Overlord (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14523)
- Flesh Spell Fortify Unarmed Damage (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14361)
- Daedric Artifacts Overlord (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15667)
- Craftable Scythes (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17821)
